    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute gem with you! Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, and it\u2019s truly spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! It drives like an absolute dream and I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
